00:04:40.710 --> 00:04:48.400
It was released for Xbox 360, PlayStation 3 and PC. 

00:04:48.500 --> 00:04:52.050
Probably, it is one of the richest collector's editions for 2012 in terms of content.

00:04:52.060 --> 00:04:57.800
A fair opinion since Borderlands 2 is an amazing and crazy,crazy,crazy game!

